Package: ThresholdR
Type: Package
Title: ThresholdR for denoising ADT data in CITEseq experiments
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Mohammad", "Oliaeimotlagh",
      email = "oliaeimm@pennmedicine.upenn.edu",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Noise usually contaminates ADT data in CITEseq experiments, which needs to be removed for better cell type annotation and downstream analyses. ThresholdR achieves this through fitting Gaussian Mixture Model (GMM)s.
